{"article_id":"NlHtWsDjZpi90Vf9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Supreme Court on Friday blocked the Trump administration from immediately enforcing a strict new asylum policy , in a 5-4 decision","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"that marks the second legal setback this week for efforts","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"to tighten immigration rules .","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"The court , in a brief written order , denied a bid","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"to begin enforcing an asylum ban for any immigrants","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"who illegally cross the U.S.-Mexico border .","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"The decision leaves in place lower-court rulings","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"that blocked the administration from automatically denying asylum to people","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"who do not go through official border crossings .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"An open-ended nationwide injunction on enforcement","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"issued by a San Francisco-based federal judge this week","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"prompted the Justice Department to seek immediate relief from the Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Chief Justice John Roberts provided the critical vote against the administration Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"siding with the four liberal justices .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Newly confirmed Justice Brett Kavanaugh and three other conservatives on the bench sided with the administration ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"the order said .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"despite having surgery in New York on Friday","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"to remove cancerous nodules in her lung ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"apparently voted with the majority ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"avoiding a 4-4 tie .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"The current legal challenge originated in California ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"where the 9th U.S . Circuit Court of Appeals also recently ruled against the administration","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"the policy was likely \" inconsistent \" with existing law .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Trump has said","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"he was acting in response to caravans of migrants","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"making their way to the border .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"The Supreme Court order comes","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"after a federal judge in a separate case took the extraordinary step this week","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"of ordering","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that asylum seekers","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who sued","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"after their deportation","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"be returned to the U.S.","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"to have their claims heard anew .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"U.S. District Judge Emmet Sullivan ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"in doing so ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"blocked policies","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that could prevent immigrants","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"who claim to have suffered gang violence or domestic abuse in their home countries","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"from seeking asylum .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"The White House said in response","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"that Wednesday ' s ruling \" will further overwhelm our immigration courts with meritless cases ,","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"making the existing massive backlog even worse . \"","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"Despite setbacks in the courts ,","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"the administration is moving forward with other changes .","depth":3},{"id":47,"text":"Department of Homeland Security Secretary Kirstjen Nielsen announced Thursday","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"that the U.S. has secured an agreement with Mexico","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"so that immigrants","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"claiming asylum","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"will be returned to Mexico","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"as their cases are processed","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"-- a bid","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"to end the practice","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"known as \" catch-and-release . \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Nielsen made the announcement at a House Judiciary Committee hearing ,","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"telling the committee","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"that the goal is to crack down on migrants","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"falsely claiming asylum ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"only to be released into the U.S.","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"and escape the radar of immigration officials .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" But by the time the courts have issued their orders ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"most of these illegal aliens have vanished within our country for good , \"","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"\" They have escaped the law ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"undermined the system ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"and made it harder for us to actually help real asylum-seekers","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"by flooding the system with false claims . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":137,"left":113,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":110,"right":112,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":96,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":93,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":89,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":80,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":77,"right":79,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":71,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":0,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":3,"right":72,"relation":"ela